{
  "stem": "7684.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Chaim had to dance for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he asked me to dance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] that's the way I met Chaim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I speak in schools, I say always, and he fell instantly in love with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody laughs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I feel happy that somebody laughs on that moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So after that, I saw these three boys that I know from hometown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they say-- told us where we sleep, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I don't-- not somebody officially tells you where you sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If the girls are all [INAUDIBLE], they tell you where you sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they told us, do you know what that fire is?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And see, that's my-- my wife a few months ago, or a few weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Van Damme, ?] one of the-- he had a baby from nine months old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other one had a baby from two years old, that his wife went already there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, when you come to a place like that, you cannot-- you cannot understand that there is such a thing, that all these people when you came, they are now burning, and that they are dead, and that you were sorting their clothes.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I don't think that-- that came through my-- that I could understand what was going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, I-- I tell you, it took me a long, long time to understand that I was in a death camp and that I was alive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because how come that these people are not alive?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- what was the-- what was my luck that I could do all these things?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I've-- and I-- that they let me live and these people-- it is something that you couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
